{"tid":664543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休警司女兒涉藏大麻    辯方指被告患過度活躍待索報告","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T12:48:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"968b8b8e7cc670eb7f3b660a50accd5c2db14d59","tid":664543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"退休高級警司狄志堅的19歲女兒狄曉晴去年7月5日涉藏大麻草被捕，被控一項管有危險藥物罪。案件今於粉嶺裁判法院開審，雖早前兩次去信律政司申請簽保守行為均被拒，今天辯方申請押後，以便再去信律政司申請或能以簽保守行為方式處理案件，案件押後至6月26日再訊，以待律政司回覆及裁判官索閱被告校園精神科醫生報告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告證實患上專注力失調與過度活躍症，於今年3月初次向其就讀大學的精神科醫生求醫，而該學校的精神科報告在上周四才發出，故現需時索閱文件。<br />\n<br />\n就讀美國東北大學的19歲被告狄曉晴被控於2017年7月5日，在上水中心商場內藏有兩袋分別有4.9及3.8克大麻草，共有約8.7克大麻草。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1215081/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1215081%2F&d=H1LxElxrqP%2BjdOOa2Pcn9ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=32625cde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1215081%2F&h=be9ac62d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1215081/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蝴蝶效應?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636711f129db3619eddaba2afc42cc97363c50f3","tid":664543,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"最衰占中"},{"pid":"0fed5c960ae8c74bb96f40b0ef6381b34a24e60b","tid":664543,"uid":121672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636711f129db3619eddaba2afc42cc97363c50f3","tid":664543,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"最衰占中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"個女都感受到"},{"pid":"21607d386a98dad415f4da11b5228d9bcba9bf96","tid":664543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}